OL,3,CCould much-missed presenters soon be
OL,4,Cback on BBC News?
OL,6,GOne of the messiest aspects of the
OL,7,Gmerger of the two BBC News channels
OL,8,Glast year could be resolved, according
OL,9,Gto a report by The Sunday Times.
OL,11,FFive female news presenters ` Martine
OL,12,FCroxall, Karin Giannone, Geeta Guru-
OL,13,FMurthy, Kasia Madera and Annita
OL,14,FMcVeigh ` were taken off air last
OL,15,Fspring, having lost out on new
OL,16,Fpositions on the newly merged BBC News
OL,17,Fservice.
OL,19,FThe newspaper says the BBC could be
OL,20,Fsoon offering them new roles, to avoid
OL,21,Fany legal action.
