OL,3,CCould much-missed presenters soon be
OL,4,Cback on BBC News?
OL,6,FThe changes to BBC News in April 2023
OL,7,Fresulted in most of the former BBC
OL,8,FWorld News daytime and evening
OL,9,Fpresenter line-up being retained.
OL,10,FPresenters on the old domestic service
OL,11,Flost out, although both Jane Hill and
OL,12,FBen Brown secured presenting duties on
OL,13,FBBC One.
OL,15,FThe farcical situation has resulted in
OL,16,Fthe BBC paying the five presenters
OL,17,Ftheir full salary, while trying to cut
OL,18,Fcosts in BBC News. At the same time, a
OL,19,Fnumber of presenter vacancies have
OL,20,Fbecome available.
