OL,3,CCould much-missed presenters soon be
OL,4,Cback on BBC News?
OL,6,FThe BBC has drafted in freelancers,
OL,7,Fsuch as the former Al Jazeera
OL,8,Fpresenter Lauren Taylor. It has also
OL,9,Frecruited Kylie Pentelow, a former BBC
OL,10,Fregional presenter who rejoined the
OL,11,Fbroadcaster in 2023 after raising her
OL,12,Fprofile at ITV, moving from regional
OL,13,Fto national news presentation.
OL,15,FIt's not the first time the BBC has
OL,16,Fbeen accused of sidelining older
OL,17,Ffemale presenters. Back in 2009,
OL,18,Faddressing concerns that women of a
OL,19,Fcertain age were being pushed out of
OL,20,Fbroadcasting, Fiona Armstong was
OL,21,Frecruited to present bulletins on the
OL,22,FBBC News Channel.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/6
