OL,6,FArmstrong later said the move was a
OL,7,F'token gesture by the BBC' after it
OL,8,Femerged she had only been offered 30
OL,9,Fdays a year to cover for other
OL,10,Fpresenters.
OL,12,FThis time, the five presenters have
OL,13,Fstood together and have the support of
OL,14,Fthe NUJ and many viewers. The Sunday
OL,15,FTimes reports that the BBC is
OL,16,Fpreparing to complete a 'reverse
OL,17,Fferret' to avoid legal action and
OL,18,Fdisastrous PR.
