OL,6,FAn insider is quoted as confirming
OL,7,Fthat the BBC is in fact short of
OL,8,Fpresenters and that a number of on-
OL,9,Fscreen roles will be created this year
OL,10,Fin the run-up to the election.
OL,12,FThe BBC has recently lost three high-
OL,13,Fprofile presenters:
