OL,3,CCould much-missed presenters soon be
OL,4,Cback on BBC News?
OL,6,
OL,7,F George Alagiah, former presenter of
OL,8,Fthe BBC News at Six, who died in 2023.
OL,9,F Yalda Hakim, who was moved to the
OL,10,Fevening news slot on BBC News,
OL,11,Fdeparted for Sky News in the autumn.
OL,12,F Suspended BBC News at Ten presenter
OL,13,FHuw Edwards is not expected to return,
OL,14,Fwith Clive Myrie tipped to succeed
OL,15,FEdwards, in turn creating a vacancy
OL,16,Felsewhere in the organisation.
OL,18,FThe BBC has refused to comment on The
OL,19,FSunday Times report. And none of the
OL,20,Faffected presenters issued any comment
OL,21,Fand would be not expected to do so
OL,22,Fwhile HR processes are carried out.
